title: DEFENSE OF THE ELVES - Third Age Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
Third Age Total War Mod Gameplay - Mordor, Isengard, and Rhun have marched out a massive invasion force.  The Silvan and High Elves gather what troops they can find and prepare to defend their borders.  The invaders have an army of 12,000 strong, and Elves are at about 4,000 strong.  Enjoy the Battle :D

This is a custom scenario made by Synn of the Dark Cloud.  Thanks for the battle :D


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
